Everyone wants to have great sex. Now everyone can!
Written by Dr. Debby Herbenick and Grant Stoddard, two of the world's most highly esteemed sex experts, Great in Bed is a guide to fantastic sex that takes a "he said/she said" point of view, so couples can learn how to properly communicate their desires with their partner.

Perfect for a couple just getting together, or one who's been together for years, Great in Bed teaches sexual confidence, positive self-image, and multiple skills so readers can learn how to bring their bedroom escapades to the next level.

293 Pages

This is a stimulating new guide to healthy sexuality that's both tantalising and technical. For such a popular subject, it's amazing how little many people really know about sex. That's where Jane Bogart comes in. As a frequent guest on television networks like MTV, "Sex Jane" has become one of the most respected international "sexperts". In "Sexploration", she employs her frank, easygoing style to give readers the ultimate sex education course - a combination of scientific information, how-to descriptions and interactive activities that will help readers put their sexual histories in perspective, get them in touch with their true desires and chart a course for how to achieve these goals in the future. Full of great tips and illuminating real-life testimonies, "Sexploration" is for people of all ages who want to get in touch with their erotic side.
